title: LF Duo partner
body:
Would love to Duo with anybody, would be nice if you had Skype/TeamSpeak or any voice comms.
Add me up in-game, and send me a message too! :)
Currently Silver 4, played 12 ranked so far, I am able to play any role but Mid and Support is my specialty.
(Hoping to reach Gold before season ends, and hoping to climb to Plat)

Any players that have tips and tricks on fantastic warding places, would love it if you pop a message down below.

Add me in-game and shoot me a message!
-AllGudNamesRGone
